{"article_id":"uppOI8HBIQzxVVZV","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Strategists say","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Romney will continue to attack the president over the mandate .","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"Romney 's tax trap","depth":2},{"id":3,"text":"The path","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"Mitt Romney needs to walk","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"on health care","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"got a little bit narrower Monday ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"when one of the Republican ' s top advisers declared in a TV interview","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"the presumptive GOP nominee agrees with the Obama administration","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that the individual mandate","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"to buy health insurance","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"is a penalty , not a tax .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"The comments by Romney strategist Eric Fehrnstrom go to the core of the political clash","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"that has unfolded between President Barack Obama and the GOP since last week ' s Supreme Court ruling on the Affordable Care Act .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"In that case , the Court ruled","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"that the law","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"known as Obamacare","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"is constitutional under Congress ' s power","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"to tax","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"- a decision","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Republicans have brandished as proof","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"that the president broke his promise","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"not to raise taxes .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"Republican outside-spending groups such as American Crossroads and Americans For Prosperity have already launched high-dollar ad campaigns","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"pummeling Obama","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"for raising taxes .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"\" Now it ' s official :","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"Obama increased taxes on struggling families , \"","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"one Crossroads ad says .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"\" President Obama breaks another promise . \"","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Romney has been conspicuously quiet on the issue for the obvious reason","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"that as governor of Massachusetts , he imposed a health insurance mandate of his own .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"For that reason , his campaign has avoided addressing explicitly","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"whether a mandate is the same thing as a tax .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"That changed","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"when Fehrnstrom stepped directly onto a political land mine on MSNBC .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Asked by anchor Chuck Todd","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"whether Romney \" agrees with the president \"","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"that \" you should not call the tax penalty a tax ,","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"you should call it a penalty or a fee or a fine , \"","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Fehrnstrom answered :","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"\" That ' s correct . \"","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"To Democrats , the comment looked like a get-out-of-jail-free card for the White House .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"If Romney agrees","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"that the mandate is not a tax ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"they argued ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"then Obama can ' t fairly be attacked","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"for raising middle-class taxes .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"The Obama campaign blasted out clips of Fehrnstrom ' s interview","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"and deputy campaign manager Stephanie Cutter declared on Twitter :","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"\" Well , that clears it up . \"","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Republicans argue","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"the reality is more complicated , at least politically .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"Strategists familiar with the Romney campaign ' s thinking say","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"there ' s a recognition","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Fehrnstrom","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"- an aide","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"known for his closeness to the candidate -","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"fumbled the message .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"That would mark the second highly public stumble for Fehrnstrom ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"who previously drew criticism","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"for saying","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"Romney could adjust his public image after the GOP primary , like an \" Etch A Sketch . \"","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"But going forward , strategists say","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"Romney intends to continue attacking Obama over the ACA ,","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"including the mandate .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"The argument is , essentially , that Obama can pick his poison :","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"either admit","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"that the mandate is a tax ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"or acknowledge","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that the law is unconstitutional .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Romney ' s personal view of the mandate is secondary .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"\" The Supreme Court left President Obama with two choices :","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"the federal individual mandate in ' Obamacare ' is either a constitutional tax or an unconstitutional penalty , \"","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"spokeswoman Amanda Henneberg said .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"\" Romney thinks","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"it is an unconstitutional penalty .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"What is President Obama ' s position :","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"Is his federal mandate unconstitutional","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"or is it a tax ? \"","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":159,"left":81,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":158,"left":2,"right":157,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":157,"left":107,"right":156,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"le